data.description: Welcome to Your Dream Home!    Nestled in a serene neighborhood with Hill Country views, this exceptional 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom ranch-style home is a true gem. Boasting a unique blend of comfort and luxury, this property offers a lifestyle of unparalleled relaxation and entertainment.     Key Features:     Bedrooms: 3   Bathrooms: 3     Converted Garage:  Transformed into an additional 444 square feet of living space, the converted garage opens up endless possibilities. Ideal for a home office, gym, or guest suite, this versatile area seamlessly integrates with the home's design.     Extended Driveway:  Park up to 4 cars with ease on the extended driveway, complete with an electrical station for electric cars-an eco-friendly touch for modern living.     Outdoor Oasis:  Step into your backyard paradise featuring an extended back patio, pool, and deck. Lounge in style, host barbecues, or simply unwind by the fire pit. The kids' playground adds an extra layer of family-friendly fun, while a convenient shed keeps your outdoor essentials organized.     Interior Elegance:  Inside, experience the grandeur of cathedral ceilings adorned with wood pillars and accent beams. A floor-to-ceiling fireplace with stone detailing serves as the focal point, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.      This home combines luxury with practicality.       Why Choose This Home?    Versatile living spaces for your unique needs  Electric outlet prime for car charging station.  Stunning outdoor retreat for relaxation and entertainment  Exquisite interior features for a touch of elegance  Don't miss the chance to make this extraordinary property your own. Schedule a viewing today and embark on a new chapter of luxurious living!
